樣，冇佢地嘅努力都唔會令民主得以喺世界擴散</blockquote>"},{"pid":"806293ecb4d43605d027e047bd8032483c049922","tid":1288861,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"真係好病出唔到sorry"},{"pid":"276afe19fc383748e7c4825cb8ad2a27991cec99","tid":1288861,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:02:35.000Z","msg":"This is yr facebook?"}]}